388
00:25:25,166 --> 00:25:26,625
[gerbang terbuka]

389
00:25:26,708 --> 00:25:28,708
[musik yang menegangkan diputar]

390
00:25:44,458 --> 00:25:45,958
[pengemudi] Wah.

